<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cake's Kingdom | Premium Bakery Karachi</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --pink: #ff85a2;
            --dark-pink: #e66a8a;
            --cream: #fff5f7;
            --gold: #d4af37;
            --text: #333;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: var(--text); background: var(--cream); }

        /* Navigation */
        header {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px 10%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 26px; color: var(--pink); text-decoration: none; }
        nav a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); margin-left: 25px; font-weight: 500; transition: 0.3s; }
        nav a:hover { color: var(--pink); }

        /* Common Section Styling */
        section { padding: 80px 10%; min-height: 100vh; }
        h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 40px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; color: var(--pink); }

        /* 1. HOME PAGE */
        .home {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551024601-bec78aea704b?q=80&w=1964&auto=format&fit=crop');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .home h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 60px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .cta-btn { background: var(--pink); color: white; padding: 15px 35px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--dark-pink); transform: scale(1.05); }

        /* 2. ABOUT PAGE */
        .about { background: white; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 50px; align-items: center; }
        .about-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 20px 20px 0 var(--pink); }
        .rating-badge { background: var(--gold); color: white; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: inline-block; }

        /* 3. MENU PAGE */
        .menu-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; }
        .menu-item { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center; transition: 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .menu-item:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        .menu-item img { width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .price { color: var(--gold); font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; }

        /* 4. CONTACT PAGE */
        .contact { background: white; }
        .contact-flex { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 40px; }
        .info-card { background: var(--cream); padding: 30px; border-radius: 20px; }
        form input, form textarea { width: 100%; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; outline: none; }
        form button { width: 100%; padding: 15px; background: var(--pink); border: none; color: white; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; }

        /* Floating WhatsApp */
        .wa-float { position: fixed; bottom: 30px; right: 30px; background: #25d366; width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); z-index: 1000; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about, .contact-flex { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .home h1 { font-size: 35px; }
            nav { display: none; } /* Mobile par nav chupa di (Simple rakha hai) */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <a href="#home" class="logo">Cake's Kingdom 🍰</a>
        <nav>
            <a href="#home">Home</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#menu">Menu</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="home" id="home">
        <h1>Sweetness Delivered</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">Karachi's Favorite Customized Cakes & Pastries</p>
        <a href="#menu" class="cta-btn">View Menu</a>
    </section>

    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="about-img">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557925923-33b27f891f88?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Bakery">
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
            <span class="rating-badge">4.9 ★ (273+ Google Reviews)</span>
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Cake's Kingdom is more than just a bakery; it's a place where we turn your dreams into edible art. Located in the heart of Buffer Zone, Karachi, we have been serving happiness for years with 24/7 service.</p>
            <br>
            <p><b>📍 Location:</b> R 708, Sector 15-A/5, Buffer Zone, Karachi</p>
            <p><b>⏰ Hours:</b> Open 24 Hours (7 Days a week)</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="menu" id="menu">
        <h2>Our Bestsellers</h2>
        <div class="menu-grid">
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578985545062-69928b1d9587?w=500&auto=format" alt="Chocolate Cake">
                <h3>Customized Birthday Cake</h3>
                <p>Starts from</p>
                <p class="price">Rs. 2,500</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563729784474-d77dbb933a9e?w=500&auto=format" alt="Cupcakes">
                <h3>Premium Cupcakes (6pcs)</h3>
                <p>Mixed Flavors</p>
                <p class="price">Rs. 1,200</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464349095431-e9a21285b5f3?w=500&auto=format" alt="Pastries">
                <h3>Wedding Special</h3>
                <p>Per Pound</p>
                <p class="price">Rs. 3,500</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact" id="contact">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <div class="contact-flex">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Contact Info</h3>
                <br>
                <p><b>Phone:</b> 012345....</p>
                <p><b>Email:</b> hello@cakeskingdom.com</p>
                <br>
                <p><b>Services:</b></p>
                <p>✅ Curbside Pickup</p>
                <p>✅ No-contact Delivery</p>
                <p>✅ Custom Designs</p>
            </div>
            <form action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_ID" method="POST">
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Tell us about your cake requirements..." required></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Send Order Request</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <a href="https://wa.me/923453833833" class="wa-float" target="_blank">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6b/WhatsApp.svg" width="35" alt="WhatsApp">
    </a>

    <footer style="background: #333; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 30px;">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Cake's Kingdom Karachi | Designed for Sweet Lovers</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
